{"tid":2395591,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2021 DSE自修生] 中文三份卷 MOCK","createTime":"2021-02-05T03:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T10:42:00.000Z","uid":125535,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b6ba8f410ea1feb95976eb7e68b323622f357a","tid":2395591,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:53:35.000Z","msg":"-----------------------------------<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"blue\">倒數77日</span></span>------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n係咪好想有人幫手改作文?<br />\n想知自己綜合邊到做得唔夠好?<br />\n啊!!!好想有人改卷啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家中文mock要人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地呢次都搵咗日校老師幫自修生們改卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情如下:<br />\n<br />\n卷一&amp;二模擬試-<br />\n日期: 10/02/2021 (星期三)<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">*截止報名日期: 08/02/2021*</span><br />\n<br />\n時間:<br />\nTimeslot A:<br />\n10:00-11:30 Paper 1<br />\n12:00-13:30 Paper 2<br />\n<br />\nTimeslot B:<br />\n14:00-15:30 Paper 1<br />\n16:00-17:30 Paper 2<br />\n<br />\n-卷三模擬試-<br />\n日期: 17/02/2021 (星期三)<br />\n時間: <br />\nTimeslot A:<br />\n09:30-11:00 Paper 3<br />\n<br />\nTimeslot B:<br />\n12:00-13:30 Paper 3<br />\n<br />\n-解卷-<br />\n日期: 26/02/2021(星期五)<br />\n時間: 16:00-19:00<br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅巴絲可以係google form到留低聯絡方法，會再PM大家詳情,名額先到先得啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/bkioDi12hHs1c5V78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FbkioDi12hHs1c5V78&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9Ec0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=49fd1b18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/bkioDi12hHs1c5V78</a><br />\n<br />\n*自修生優先，如果最後仲有位可以俾埋中六同學仔*<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申1:出席到兩日(10/02/2021 &amp; 17/02/2021)嘅報名者可